fr.expression4j.core.impl
Class CatalogImpl

java.lang.Object
  fr.expression4j.core.impl.CatalogImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Catalog
public class CatalogImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements Catalog

Implementation of catalog interface. 

 All catalog store the default functions derived from java Math class:
        - abs(x)
  - acos(x)
  - asin(x)
  - atan(x)
  - ceil(x)
  - cos(x)
  - cosh(x)
  - exp(x)
  - floor(x)
  - log(x)
  - random()
  - sin(x)
  - sinh(x)
  - sqrt(x)
  - tan(x)  
 
 and default constant
  - pi = 3.14159 ...
  - e  = 2,71828182845904523536028747135266249
